TY  - JOUR
T1  - Reply—Consider the Principal Finding: A Reply to William T. Ross
AU  - Hogarth, Robin M.
AU  - Makridakis, Spyros
Y1  - 1988/05/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.34.5.672
